{"tid":981971,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【add名人時尚】陳偉霆坐頭排 Got7成員帥氣現身男裝騷","createTime":"2019-01-14T17:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T17:13:51.000Z","uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bebbc3f1316a30f5b1667374e1c720138ad5f940","tid":981971,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"【add名人時尚】陳偉霆坐頭排 Got7成員帥氣現身男裝騷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190113/large/1547363839_7b9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190113%2Flarge%2F1547363839_7b9b.jpg&h=808200d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019 米蘭男裝周揭幕，品牌大騷場上的VIP 位置的明星面孔自然不可少。<br />\n<br />\n近年力求年輕化的騷場，有兩位男士成為焦點：代言人陳偉霆，以及品牌去年被Zegna Group收購的Thom Browne 。「他是我的新好友，我愛我們的友誼。」Thom Brown 坐首行現身支持兼表態。<br />\n<br />\n首行明星還有：美國明星Charlie Plummer、韓國男子組合Got7的兩位成員BamBam和Marc Tuan，更首次有女性明星名人：名模Winnie Harlow 和Maria Borges。品牌今次在米蘭地標中央火車站舉行，廣場化身為迷宮一般縱橫交錯的騷場，新裝柔和又不失正裝設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190113/large/1547363857_4848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190113%2Flarge%2F1547363857_4848.jpg&h=80db3f07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳偉霆是品牌的代言人，現身男裝騷撐場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190113/large/1547363857_0eaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190113%2Flarge%2F1547363857_0eaf.jpg&h=0481a4b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3133535c818d3c01a5eab13a0f2da68d256a3ee7","tid":981971,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}